name: SocialDeal
overview:
SocialDeal.net allows consumers to earn cash back from their purchases as well as earning cash back from purchases made by their social graph as a result of their recommendations.

SocialDeal.net aggregates deals and coupons from a variety of name brand merchants and ecommerce retailers such as Macys.com, puma.com and Target.com among others. When a user makes a purchase from a SocialDeal.net partner they earn cash back.

In addition if a user finds a deal or coupon that they feel would be of interest to their social graph they can use Facebook Likes (branded as “Recommend”) or tweets to share the deal. Any members of the user’s social graph that purchase earn cash back for themselves, if they joined, as well as the person that shared the deal originally.
